resources.string: XML Translator Free i taea e whakapumautia te hononga ipurangi. Kia e hono koe ki te whatunga, me te ngana anō.
Tenei translation ka nui ake ta koutou 3000 huru rohe rā.
Waho te rokiroki, me te e wātea ana.
Tēnā maunga writable rokiroki waho pāpāho i roto i te tikanga ki te whakamahi i tēnei taupānga.
Te pānui i waho whakaaetanga e tika ana ki te pānui i te tono raraunga.
Te tuhituhi i waho whakaaetanga e tika ana ki te tuhituhi ki te tono i te kōnae.
Te pānui Rokiroki Waho whakaaetanga ka taea tēnei taupānga ki te pānui i nui raraunga taupānga. Tēnā tukua tenei whakaaetanga i roto i te i ngā Tautuhinga Taupānga.
Tuhituhi Rokiroki Waho whakaaetanga ka taea tēnei taupānga ki te taonga nui raraunga taupānga. Tēnā tukua tenei whakaaetanga i roto i te i ngā Tautuhinga Taupānga.
Tena, te tīpako i te rerekē ngā kōnae xml.
Tēnā tomo i te kuputuhi i roto i te hōputu XML.
Tei runga i te nui o te whakamāoritanga, e tenei tukanga taea e te pau i te nui nui o te raraunga pūkoro.
Na reira, kei te tohutohu te reira e whiwhi koe i te here ranei unmetered hononga whatunga i mua i timata to koutou translation.
